{"tid":2514642,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成日都好想返屋企","createTime":"2021-05-03T11:31:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T12:27:30.000Z","uid":308795,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e642f41066b0d1499328fb0080a4d0fd73d4b67e","tid":2514642,"uid":308795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:31:48.000Z","msg":"利申返唔喺香港讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走之前同屋企關係唔算好好<br />\n以為自己唔會掛住<br />\n但事實係過到嚟成日自己夜媽媽喊苦喊忽<br />\n好掛住屋企人同朋友<br />\n但又唔想屋企人擔心自己唯有收收埋埋<br />\n尤其最近零舍多事發生<br />\n身體又越嚟越差<br />\n每去到啲辛苦位就會諗起細細個有咩病痛嘅時候都有屋企人喺身邊陪住自己<br />\n好掛住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日眼淚鼻涕撈飯好辛苦"},{"pid":"4c59f5cda3eb730a4f4d5dfe4f88a271e36e4e64","tid":2514642,"uid":366655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"quit咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4180c27d046bea84182051ed74b823cce69cbda","tid":2514642,"uid":352900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:35:58.000Z","msg":"唔可以返香港讀？<br />\n<br />\n你又凍 又寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033971eb58a7b4122910afa73537ee573ef18f30","tid":2514642,"uid":308795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c59f5cda3eb730a4f4d5dfe4f88a271e36e4e64","tid":2514642,"uid":366655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:33:02.000Z","msg":"quit咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁辛苦過到嚟"},{"pid":"7134b64a6c45da6d80021dd79bf25b8201e34aa1","tid":2514642,"uid":17211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:37:02.000Z","msg":"你返去就會後悔"},{"pid":"87a3b73f22f39476b8dd1c247ee3cd4b45ccbdac","tid":2514642,"uid":308795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4180c27d046bea84182051ed74b823cce69cbda","tid":2514642,"uid":352900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:35:58.000Z","msg":"唔可以返香港讀？<br />\n<br />\n你又凍 又寂寞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:41:05.000Z","msg":"就係覺得我喺香港太垃圾 所以掟我過嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5ffd127cce87ae467a56ed66a0cad42bcf80267","tid":2514642,"uid":23495,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:41:27.000Z","msg":"唔建議返<br />\n孤獨呢個過程你始終都要面對<br />\n始終有一日 朋友屋企人 都陪唔到你<br />\n人大咗你就明 <br />\n<br />\n邊度讀書？ 如果你係英國呢啲熱門地方<br />\n其實大把香港人可以識"},{"pid":"a2799d4ace33d256133cf6d2d64b737a90825de8","tid":2514642,"uid":308795,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7134b64a6c45da6d80021dd79bf25b8201e34aa1","tid":2514642,"uid":17211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:37:02.000Z","msg":"你返去就會後悔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實全部朋友同屋企人都同我講走到已經好幸福 成日話咩你就好啦咁自由<br />\n可能係我太貪心 但我真係好掛住大家"},{"pid":"94b43f66246b7ea8ef1d57fdd7236e93bab46021","tid":2514642,"uid":228213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e642f41066b0d1499328fb0080a4d0fd73d4b67e","tid":2514642,"uid":308795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:31:48.000Z","msg":"利申返唔喺香港讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走之前同屋企關係唔算好好<br />\n以為自己唔會掛住<br />\n但事實係過到嚟成日自己夜媽媽喊苦喊忽<br />\n好掛住屋企人同朋友<br />\n但又唔想屋企人擔心自己唯有收收埋埋<br />\n尤其最近零舍多事發生<br />\n身體又越嚟越差<br />\n每去到啲辛苦位就會諗起細細個有咩病痛嘅時候都有屋企人喺身邊陪住自己<br />\n好掛住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />成日眼淚鼻涕撈飯好辛苦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:44:57.000Z","msg":"會唔會可以改變下生活方式，係咪建立唔起圈子？"},{"pid":"92c71f0f80259cd0759b13da45ca9063c30ebd96","tid":2514642,"uid":308795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94b43f66246b7ea8ef1d57fdd7236e93bab460